2-1-ronaldo-stunner-decides-santiago-bernabeu-trophy |date=24 August 2017 | title =2-1: Ronaldo stunner decides Santiago Bernab\u00e9u Trophy |accessdate=24 August 2017 |website=Realmadrid.com |last=Navarro |first=Alberto |location=Madrid, Spain |publisher=Real Madrid Club de F\u00fatbol }}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== Individual honours ==\n=== Selections for the best player or forward ===\n==== World ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=20%|Award\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\"|Edition / year\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Result\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Ref(s)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|[[Ballon d'Or]]\n|[[2008 Ballon d'Or|2008]], [[2016 Ballon d'Or|2016]], and [[2017 Ballon d'Or|2017]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news |first=Mike |last=Norrish |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/3541051/Manchester-Uniteds-Cristiano-Ronaldo-wins-Ballon-dOr-and-says-best-is-yet-to-come-Football.html |title=Manchester United's Cristiano Ronaldo wins Ballon d'Or and says best is yet to come |date=2 December 2008 |accessdate=8 December 2019 |work=The Daily Telegraph}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Gregg Roughley and agencies |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/dec/02/ronaldo-manchesterunited |title=Ronaldo beats off Messi and Torres to scoop Ballon d'Or |date=2 December 2008 |accessdate=8 December 2019 |website=[[TheGuardian.com]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Guardian sport and agencies |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/dec/12/cristiano-ronaldo-ballon-dor-fourth-lionel-messi |title=Cristiano Ronaldo wins Ballon d'Or for the fourth time |date=12 December 2016 |accessdate=8 December 2019 |website=[[TheGuardian.com]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Charlie |last=Eccleshare |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/12/12/ballon-dor-2016-live-updates-cristiano-ronaldo-leo-messi-go/ |title=Cristiano Ronaldo beats Lionel Messi to Ballon d'Or 2016 as Jamie Vardy and Gareth Bale make top 10