stiano-ronaldo-mahou-five-star-player-in-december|title=Cristiano Ronaldo, Mahou Five Star player in December|website=Realmadrid.com|publisher=Real Madrid Club de F\u00fatbol|date=15 January 2018|accessdate=15 June 2018|location=Madrid, Spain}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2018/04/cristiano-ronaldo-the-mahou-five-star-player-for-march|title=Cristiano Ronaldo, the Mahou five star player for March|website=Realmadrid.com|publisher=Real Madrid Club de F\u00fatbol|date=13 April 2018|accessdate=15 June 2018|location=Madrid, Spain}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==== Italy ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=20%|Award\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\"|Edition / year\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Result\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Ref(s)\n|-\n|[[Serie A Awards|Serie A Award]] for Most Valuable Player\n|[[2018\u201319 Serie A|2018\u201319]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.football-italia.net/138193/ronaldo-mvp-serie-awards |title=Ronaldo MVP in Serie A Awards |publisher=Football Italia |date=18 May 2019 |accessdate=18 May 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Serie A Footballer of the Year]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Serie A|2019]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.football-italia.net/147170/ronaldo-crowned-serie-best-player|title=Ronaldo crowned Serie A best player|date=2 December 2019|publisher=Football Italia|accessdate=2 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Serie A]] MVP of the Month\n|[[2019\u201320 Serie A#Players' awards|1/2020]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.legaseriea.it/en/press/news/info/cristiano-ronaldo-mvp-for-january |publisher=Serie A |accessdate=31 January 2020 |date=31 January 2020 |title=Cristiano Ronaldo MVP For January}}</ref>\n|}\n\n; Juventus\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=20%|Award\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\"|Edition / year\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Result\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Ref(s)\n|-\n|{{abbr|[[Most valuab