hs.de/iffhs-awards-2019-the-worlds-best-top-goal-scorer-cristiano-ronaldo-portugalfc-juventus/|title=IFFHS AWARDS 2019 \u2013 THE WORLD'S BEST TOP GOAL SCORER (INTERNATIONAL GOALS) : CRISTIANO RONALDO (PORTUGAL/FC JUVENTUS)|date=1 January 2020|publisher=International Federation of Football History & Statistics (IFFHS)|accessdate=3 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|IFFHS [[International Federation of Football History & Statistics#IFFHS World's Best Top Division Goal Scorer|World's Best Top Division Scorer]]\n|2014 and 2015\n|<ref name=IFFHS /><ref name=FRIFFHS />\n|-\n|[[FIFA Club World Cup]]\n|[[2016 FIFA Club World Cup|2016]] and [[2017 FIFA Club World Cup|2017]]{{efn|Shared with [[Romarinho (footballer, born 1990)|Romarinho]] and [[Maur\u00edcio Ant\u00f4nio]].}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/clubworldcup/archive/japan2016/statistics/players/goal-scored.html|title=FIFA Club World Cup Japan 2016 {{!}} Players - Top goals|publisher=F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Football Association (FIFA)|access-date=28 June 2018|website=FIFA.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/clubworldcup/statistics/players/goal-scored.html|title=FIFA Club World Cup UAE 2017 {{!}} Players - Top goals|publisher=F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Football Association (FIFA)|access-date=4 May 2018|website=FIFA.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[UEFA European Championship]]\n|[[UEFA Euro 2012|2012]]{{efn|Ronaldo tied with five other players on goals; however, [[Fernando Torres]] registered more assists and played fewer minutes than others, thus earning the [[UEFA Euro 2012#Awards|Golden Boot]].}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2012/statistics/round=15172/players/type=topscorers/|title=UEFA EURO 2012 Statistics|publisher=UEFA|date=16 March 2015|accessdate=21 May 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"#DCE5E5\"|UEFA European Championship Silver Boot\n|[[UEFA Euro 2016|2016]]\n|<ref>{{cite news |title=France forward Antoine Griezmann wins Golden Boot |url=http://www.u