/2019\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Serie A Team of the Month: Ronaldo finally gets going for Juventus|url=https://www.whoscored.com/Articles/RgWgdFmMNEa7P2zXWvNXNg/Show/Serie-A-Team-of-the-Month-Ronaldo-finally-gets-going-for-Juventus|website=WhoScored.com|access-date=9 November 2019|last=Wright|first=Josh|date=4 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Serie A Best XI: Ronaldo joined in team of the month by Milan and Napoli players|url=https://fr.whoscored.com/Articles/o_fhXqCQckG1Dqob34HB3g/Show/Serie-A-Best-XI-Ronaldo-joined-in-team-of-the-month-by-Milan-and-Napoli-players|website=WhoScored.com|access-date=9 November 2019|last=Wright|first=Josh|date=3 March 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Selections for international sportsperson of the year ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=20%|Competition /award\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\"|Edition / year\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Result\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Ref(s)\n|-\n|[[Laureus World Sports Award for Sportsman of the Year]]\n|2009, 2014, 2015, 2017, and 2018{{efn|While playing for [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]], Ronaldo was part of the team which was nominated for [[Laureus World Sports Award for Team of the Year]] in 2009,<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://laureus17.laureus.com/awards-history/2009/nominees/team/#tab-container| title = Laureus World Team of the Year 2009 nominees| publisher = Laureus| accessdate = 24 October 2017}}{{Dead link|date=July 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.teamusa.org/News/2009/June/26/China-team-gets-sports-award | publisher = [[United States Olympic Committee]] | agency=Associated Press| accessdate = 24 October 2017 | title = China team gets sports award |date = 26 June 2009}}</ref> and in 2015,<ref name=germanywc>{{Cite web | url = http://www.espn.com/espn/story/_/id/12695150/novak-djokovic-genzebe-dibaba-germany-world-cup-team-win-laureus-awards | title = Nova