60482/juventus-man-cristiano-ronaldo-is-uefa-champions-league-player-of-the-week/ |title=Juventus man Cristiano Ronaldo is UEFA Champions League player of the week |work=Official website of [[Fox Sports Asia]] |date=16 March 2019 |accessdate=16 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|37/2017, 14/2018\n|{{nom}}\n|{{Citation needed|date=January 2020}}\n|-\n|[[Joe.ie|JOE]]'s Champions League Man of the Week\n|50/2014 and 8/2015\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.joe.ie/sport/joes-champions-league-man-of-the-week-cristiano-ronaldo-478560 |title=JOE's Champions League Man of the Week: Cristiano Ronaldo |date=2014 |accessdate=15 April 2017 |website=Joe.ie |last=Lalor |first=Eric}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.joe.ie/sport/champions-league-man-of-the-week-cristiano-ronaldo-485811 |title=Champions League man of the week: Cristiano Ronaldo |date=2015 |accessdate=6 May 2017 |website=Joe.ie |author=Joe}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==== England ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=20%|Award\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:13%;\"|Edition / year\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Result\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Ref(s)\n|-\n|[[PFA Young Player of the Year]]\n|[[2006\u201307 FA Premier League#PFA Young Player of the Year|2006\u201307]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/6582201.stm|title=Ronaldo secures PFA awards double|publisher=BBC Sport|date=22 April 2007|accessdate=24 May 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[PFA Players' Player of the Year]]\n|[[2006\u201307 FA Premier League#PFA Players' Player of the Year|2006\u201307]] and [[2007\u201308 Premier League#PFA Players' Player of the Year|2007\u201308]]\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7370319.stm|title=Ronaldo named player of the year|publisher=BBC|accessdate=28 April 2009|date=27 April 2008}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Football Writers' Association Footballer of the Year]]\n|[[2006\u201307 FA Premier League#Football Writers' Association Fo