bsite of Real Madrid<ref name=CR7onRM.com>{{cite web |title=Cristiano Ronaldo (CR7) |url=http://www.realmadrid.com/en/football/squad/cristiano-ronaldo-dos-santos |website=Realmadrid.com |location=Madrid, Spain |accessdate=21 February 2017 |publisher=Real Madrid Club de F\u00fatbol }}</ref>}}\n\n===== All-time =====\n{{For|a comprehensive listing on this topic|List of La Liga top scorers#All-time top scorers}}\n{{Updated|7 March 2020}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"1000\" style=\"font-size:95%\";\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Rank\n! scope=\"col\"| Name\n! scope=\"col\"| Goals\n! scope=\"col\"| Apps\n! scope=\"col\"| Ratio\n! scope=\"col\"| Years\n! scope=\"col\"| Club(s)\n|- align=center\n|scope=\"row\"|1\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|{{Sortname|Lionel|Messi}}|ARG}}\n|'''438'''||474||{{#expr:438/474 round 3}}||2004\u2013present||align=left| [[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n|- align=center\n|scope=\"row\"|2\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|'''Cristiano Ronaldo'''|POR}}\n|'''311'''||292||{{#expr:311/292 round 3}}||2009\u20132018||align=left| [[Real Madrid CF|Real Madrid]]\n|- align=center\n|scope=\"row\"|3\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|{{Sortname|Telmo|Zarra}}|ESP}}\n|'''251'''||278||{{#expr:251/278 round 3}}||1940\u20131955||align=left| [[Athletic Bilbao]]\n|- align=center\n|scope=\"row\"|4\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|{{Sortname|Hugo|S\u00e1nchez}}|MEX}}\n|'''234'''||347||{{#expr:234/347 round 3}}||1981\u20131994||align=left| [[Real Madrid CF|Real Madrid]], [[Rayo Vallecano]], and [[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]]\n|- align=center\n|scope=\"row\"|5\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Ra\u00fal (footballer)|Ra\u00fal]]|ESP}}\n|'''228'''||550||{{#expr:228/550 round 3}}||1994\u20132010||align=left| [[Real Madrid CF|Real Madrid]]\n|- align=center\n|}\n{{small|Source: worldfootball.net<ref>{{cite web|title=Spain \u00bb Primera Divisi\u00f3n \u00bb All-time Topscorers \u00bb rank 1 \u2013 50 |website=worldfootball.net |url=http://www.worldfootball.net/alltime_goalgetter/esp-primera-division/tore/1/ |a