3604/cristiano-ronaldo-breaks-long-standing-juventus-record/ |title=Cristiano Ronaldo breaks long-standing Juventus record |work=Official website of [[Fox Sports Asia]] |date=25 November 2018 |accessdate=25 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.timesnownews.com/sports/football/article/serie-a-2018-19-cristiano-ronaldo-shatters-long-standing-juventus-goalscoring-record/320315 |title=Cristiano Ronaldo shatters long-standing Juventus goalscoring record |work=Official website of [[Times Now]] |date=25 November 2018 |accessdate=25 November 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Former records ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Date\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:45%;\"| Record\n! scope=\"col\" width=5%|Ref\n|-\n|{{Center|2009}}\n|[[List of most expensive association football transfers|Most expensive footballer in history]]: [[Euro|\u20ac]]94&nbsp;million ([[Pound sterling|\u00a3]]80&nbsp;million){{efn|Since surpassed by [[Gareth Bale]]'s fee of \u20ac100.8&nbsp;million in 2013 (also to [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]),<ref>{{cite news |title=Bale's transfer fee revealed |url=https://www.fifa.com/world-match-centre/news/newsid/219/598/0/index.html? |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140115040606/http://www.fifa.com/world-match-centre/news/newsid/219/598/0/index.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=15 January 2014 |publisher=FIFA |agency=Agence France-Presse |date=15 October 2013 |accessdate=14 January 2014}}</ref> [[Paul Pogba]]'s \u20ac105&nbsp;million transfer fee to Manchester United in 2016, and [[Neymar]]'s \u20ac222&nbsp;million transfer fee to [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]] in 2017.}}\n|\n|-\n|\n|Most [[European Golden Shoe]]s: 4{{efn|Since surpassed by [[Lionel Messi]] (6).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/gboot.html |title=Golden Boot ('Soulier d'Or') Awards |publisher=[[Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation]] (RSSSF) |date=6 December 2018 |accessdate=30 April 20